  <brief_title>Spiriva速 in Patients With Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Tolerability and Efficacy of Spiriva速 18 Micrograms in Patients With COPD in Daily Practice</official_title>
